@MYANC SG Cde @Magashule_Ace visits the family late Reverend Emmanuel Motolla, in Hamanskraal-Pretoria, to convey condolences on behalf of the movement. Rev Motolla was the Chief Aide of His Grace, the Right Reverend, Bishop Dr B. E Lekganyane as well as the Spokesperson of ZCC. https://t.co/7dbPgHaNLD